survey_response.review_text: We found Dr. Lingaraj and his clinic via Practo, and visited him when our 3 year old child was burning with fever for over 5 days, and we were not satisfied with our then current paediatrician. Dr. Lingaraj was able to diagnose the problem quickly (within minutes of seeing her), and explained the problem in detail that completely allayed our fears. His prescription worked wonders, and within a couple of days, our child was back to normal. After a couple of more follow up visits, * *** ****** *** **** ** ** *** **** ************* ** **** ********** His clinic is clean and well sanitised, and we absolutely appreciate his patience when dealing with toddlers and their worried parents. Was very supportive and understanding. We are thankful to him, and definitely recommend him!

I would strongly recommend him as my kid was premature and under weight, he has given a proper treatment and taken a very good care of my child. He and his team has encouraged when ever we would fall short on having faith that our kid would come to a normal state and today our kid is fine because of the best treatment given by them. Thanks to Lingraj sir, Manisha mam, Ambada sir and all the sisters (Girija, Jhansi, Pavithra, Ramya, Nirmala, Ranya and Punya) who took care of my kid day and night....

I had never even heard of any pediatrician who treats every child as his own child. He is so reasonable , understanding and always available. Vaidyo narayano harihi comes out true with the case of Dr.Lingaraj. every child needs a Doc like him is what I feel. A million thanks to him for always being there for my daughter.
He is not friendly and don't respond properly..he is too fast and hurry in treating patients. ** *** ** ******* *** *** ** ****
Dr. lingraju is a good person taken a good care since the new born baby to till now. His advice & suggestion for day by day care is outstanding. Thank you!
Dr Lingaraj Sir is explained very well about baby condition and precautions and he spent valuable time with us . I will give the doctor marks 10 out of 10
Doctor never makes us feel panic in any situation. Explains reasons and tries to avoid medication aa far as possible for babies.

The best doctor I have ever met so far, I would like to recommend for child care. He will give time n right treatment for every pediatric issues. My baby gal is very lucky to have such a pediatrician , really thankful for all his support.
